notes: ItemDB (1500 items) v5: removed Defense/MagicResist from item stat modifiers.
Allowed item modifiers: primary STR/AGI/END/INT/PER and derived AttackPower/SpellPower/CritChanceRating/CritDamageRating/SpeedRating/HPRegen/ManaRegen.
Defense/MagicResist remain 'meta' via armor values (physical_armor/magic_armor) and offhands (shield/offhand).
Weapons: single 'damage' plus 'attack_interval'; no weapon range.
Stacking: all items EXCEPT gear and bags stack to 20.
Rare>=20, Epic>=40, Legendary only at level 60.
Common armor: no bonus stats (only armor values).
Consumables: 1 food, 1 drink, 1 health potion, 1 mana potion per level band.
v6: added 'icon' field referencing res://assets/icons/items/*.png; generated 232 reusable placeholder icons.
